data.description: This LOVELY 2,006+ sq. ft with 3 bedrooms, 2 bath BRICK home is situated on 2+/- acres located in Goodrich North. This home is spacious with an open concept, DREAM kitchen with NEW dishwaser (less than 6months). The 2+- acres gives opportunity for expansion and entertainment. Sip on a beverage on the covered back porch and enjoy the beauty of the peaceful country life. The roof has been replaced within the last two years and a full home generator is offered with this property. Quick access to Hwy 59 S for a quick commute to the Houston area. Look no further.  Give me a call today for your personal tour. Updated pictures coming soon.
